<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm113628896">
<term>inert pair effect</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm29656464">tendency of heavy atoms to form ions in which their valence <emphasis effect="italics">s</emphasis> electrons are not lost</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm118453184">
<term>ionic bond</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm101179264">strong electrostatic force of attraction between cations and anions in an ionic compound</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
